Lemma int_cmp_repr: forall op i j, repable_signed i -> repable_signed j -> Int.cmp op (Int.repr i) (Int.repr j) = true -> Zcmp op i j.

replace (if zeq (Int.unsigned (Int.repr i)) (Int.unsigned (Int.repr j)) then true else false) with (if zeq i j then true else false) in H1.
destruct (zeq i j); destruct (zeq (Int.unsigned (Int.repr i)) (Int.unsigned (Int.repr j))); auto.
apply Int.signed_repr in H0; rewrite Int.signed_repr_eq in H0.
match type of H with | context [if ?a then _ else _] => destruct a end; match type of H0 with | context [if ?a then _ else _] => destruct a end; omega.
rewrite (Int.signed_repr _ H) in H1; rewrite (Int.signed_repr _ H0) in H1.
repeat match type of H1 with | context [if ?a then _ else _] => destruct a end; try omegaContradiction; destruct op; auto; simpl in *; try discriminate; omega.
